OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's Chief Nursing
OL,8,FOfficer is conducting a review into
OL,9,Fthe healthcare tasks that carers can
OL,10,Fperform on people with complex medical
OL,11,Fneeds, UTV can reveal.
OL,13,FIt follows months of campaigning by
OL,14,Ffamilies after numerous direct payment
OL,15,Fcarers were told not to carry out
OL,16,Fmedical tasks.
OL,18,FHowever, a leading activist from
OL,19,FColeraine has unexpectedly been told
OL,20,Fcarers can resume nursing duties in
OL,21,Fher daughter's case.
