OL,7,FTracey Henry looks after Ellie, 22,
OL,8,Fwho needs constant care around the
OL,9,Fclock.
OL,11,FUntil April last year, she was helped
OL,12,Fby carers but that changed after the
OL,13,FNorthern Trust told her that direct
OL,14,Fpayment carers could no longer carry
OL,15,Fout nursing tasks.
OL,17,FAs a result, Tracey has barely had a
OL,18,Fbreak for nearly a year.
