OL,7,F"I don't know why I'm still here
OL,8,Fbecause I'm absolutely wrecked," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FHowever, the situation recently
OL,12,Fchanged after the Northern Trust said
OL,13,Fit sought new legal advice which has
OL,14,F"determined that a direct payment
OL,15,Farrangement can be granted, in this
OL,16,Fparticular case".
