OL,7,FTracey said: "If it can happen for us
OL,8,Fto be allowed to do that in our home,
OL,9,Fthere are thousands of families across
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland that need that help
OL,11,Fas well."
OL,13,FUTV has learned that Northern
OL,14,FIreland's Chief Nursing Officer will
OL,15,Fpublish the findings of a review into
OL,16,Fthe direct payment process in the
OL,17,Fautumn.
